# data_fetcher crontab  (supercronic format)
#
# Full fetch every 30 min during market hours Mon-Fri 08:00-22:00 UTC
# Covers XETRA (08:00-17:30 UTC) and NYSE/NASDAQ (14:30-21:00 UTC)
#
# min  hour       day  month  weekday   command
*/30   8-22        *    *      1-5       PYTHONPATH=/app python /app/data_fetcher.py
   0   23          *    *      1-5       PYTHONPATH=/app python /app/data_fetcher.py
   0    9          *    *      6         PYTHONPATH=/app python /app/data_fetcher.py
